body_html:
@jbuisson1: It's my fault (I wrote the original label_image for tf lite). The number of outputs and number of results are fixed numbers now (see https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/examples/label_image/label_image.cc#L216-L237). Quick solution: changing output_size and num_results should fix the problem.

I'll send a PR to add command options and check the output tensor later.
